snippet.title: Boom Ball 2 for Kinect Trailer
snippet.description: Bounce balls, break bricks and blow stuff up in Boom Ball 2 for Kinect, Virtual Air Guitar Company's new motion game for all ages, shapes and sizes. Includes 50 brand-new levels, manic multiball mayhem and 2-player co-op for friends and family. Go ballistic with Boom Ball!
